---
title: Fragrant Aloo Gobi with Cauliflower, Potato Curry and Cilantro
description: Aloo Gobi means 'cauliflower and potato' and is a popular South Asian curry dish! We've added a twist to the traditional recipe by roasting the cauliflower, which gives dinner a sweet pop of additional flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fragrant-aloo-gobi-9dc7ae43.jpg
